license: "MIT"
abstract: >-
  A controlled, evidence-first evaluation system for comparing a general agent
  with bounded specialist orchestration under identical tasks, tools and
  acceptance rules. Public results are deterministic fixture evidence and
  provider-free integration evidence. No real-provider benchmark has been run,
  and the prerelease does not establish production readiness.
